<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HAPPY BIRTHDAY WIVESSY 💚</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fff5f8; /* Light blush background */
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 4rem;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.3));
        }

        /* Container for your photos */
        .gallery {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .gallery img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 8px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: block;
        }

        /* The birthday wish styling */
        .wish-container {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        .main-text {
            font-size: 2.8rem; /* Big size as requested */
            color: #ff3385;    /* Pink color as requested */
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1.4;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        footer {
            margin: 40px 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>💚</header>

    <div class="gallery">
        <img src="photo1.jpg" alt="Our Moment 1">
        <img src="photo2.jpg" alt="Our Moment 2">
        <img src="photo3.jpg" alt="Our Moment 3">
        <img src="photo4.jpg" alt="Our Moment 4">
    </div>

    <div class="wish-container">
        <div class="main-text">
            Happy Birthday wivessy luv u always and won't leave you and hope you stay by my side just the same and call you my wife Have the best birthday ever ! 💚😊💫🌺
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>💫</footer>

</body>
</html>
